- Permintaan saya perlu bersedia.

670
00:46:24,551 --> 00:46:28,081
(Sijil Biasiswa)

671
00:46:35,762 --> 00:46:37,262
Jangan lupa yang...

672
00:46:37,612 --> 00:46:40,423
