687
00:47:36,451 --> 00:47:37,628
- Nasi.
- Nasi. Hei.

688
00:47:37,652 --> 00:47:38,852
- Berikan tangan awak.
- Cepatlah.

689
00:47:39,661 --> 00:47:41,395
- Jangan tumbuk kuat sangat.
